# Expo SDK 55 Anti-Patterns

Catalog of 45 anti-patterns. Severity:

- **CRIT** ships secrets, breaks production
- **ERR** wrong API, build/runtime breaks on SDK 55
- **WARN** outdated pattern, works but suboptimal
- **NIT** quality issue, easy to ignore but easy to fix

Pinned target: Expo SDK 55 (May 2026), React Native 0.83.6, React 19.2.0, Expo Router 55.0.x, Reanimated 4.2.x with `react-native-worklets/plugin`, FlashList 2.0.x, FileSystem new `File`/`Directory` API, New Architecture only (Legacy Architecture removed).

Sources: https://expo.dev/changelog/sdk-55, https://docs.expo.dev/, https://github.com/software-mansion/react-native-reanimated, https://shopify.github.io/flash-list.

